Package: sfnetworks
Version: 0.2.0
Title: Tidy Spatial Networks in R
Description: The sfnetworks package provides a tidy approach to spatial network
    analysis, in the form of classes and functions that enable a seamless interaction 
    between the network analysis package 'tidygraph' and the spatial analysis package 'sf'.
